WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:06.293
Hello, my name is Brandon, and I'm going to tell you about a visitation I had from the Lord.

00:00:06.516 --> 00:00:16.544
I don't know if it was a dream or an out-of-body experience; all I know is that it changed my life forever.

00:00:17.234 --> 00:00:22.339
I'm just going to get right into it and tell you what happened.

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:28.428
It was a normal night on July 6, 2014.

00:00:29.046 --> 00:00:32.941
I went to bed, and what happened next is mind-blowing.

00:00:35.743 --> 00:00:39.222
I want you to give me a little bit of your time.

00:00:51.379 --> 00:01:00.624
What I am about to tell you will change your life forever if you let it and meditate on what is about to happen.

00:01:00.624 --> 00:01:12.834
Earth as we know it, everything we see on a day-to-day basis, is about to change—from the biggest thing to the smallest thing.

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:23.920
This is what happened: I went to bed, and suddenly I was taken out of my body.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:33.102
In a dream, you don't smell, taste, or feel heat the way I did.

00:01:33.102 --> 00:01:44.640
Suddenly, I was standing at a courthouse, and I looked over to my right; Jesus was standing right there next to me.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:47.623
He was looking at me.

00:02:07.769 --> 00:02:08.018
I looked around, and there were people rioting and burning cars.

00:02:08.018 --> 00:02:11.817
People were destroying things, throwing things, acting crazy.

00:02:14.110 --> 00:02:22.688
I was taken aback by what I saw because I could smell the smoke and the fires.

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:32.606
I could see the courthouse on fire and mass chaos everywhere.

00:02:41.173 --> 00:02:41.439
A lady ran up to me, and I asked, "What is going on?

00:02:41.439 --> 00:02:44.697
" She said, "Don't you know?

00:02:44.697 --> 00:02:46.1000
Didn't you see?

00:02:46.1000 --> 00:02:50.270
All the Christians are gone.

00:02:55.812 --> 00:02:56.106
All the Christians are gone.

00:03:06.499 --> 00:03:06.989
" I asked, "Where did they go?

00:03:06.989 --> 00:03:08.460
What happened?

00:03:08.460 --> 00:03:14.338
" She said the aliens came and took them.

00:03:14.338 --> 00:03:20.446
Suddenly, I looked up, and there were lightning strikes all over the sky.

00:03:20.446 --> 00:03:24.507
It looked like a major storm, but there was no rain.

00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:30.754
I could see lightning in the clouds; they were active, like an electric storm.

00:03:30.754 --> 00:03:40.410
As I looked across the town, I saw fires burning in many buildings—nearly all of them.

00:03:40.410 --> 00:03:45.543
Everyone was looting and stealing, acting godless.

00:04:05.794 --> 00:04:06.423
I want to interject something: every person, even the greatest sinner, wakes up with a sense of peace they don't realize they have.

00:04:06.423 --> 00:04:12.251
I call this the prayer covering of the church.

00:04:25.439 --> 00:04:33.827
There is a covering from the praying people of the church that covers the whole world, bringing an atmosphere of peace and comfort that people don't realize is there.

00:04:33.827 --> 00:04:47.900
When the rapture of the church takes place, that prayer covering is removed for the first time.

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:01.800
There is total anarchy because people feel the void where that peace was, and they are freaking out.

00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:09.960
I felt that so strongly in the atmosphere; it was eerie and scary.

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:14.400
Suddenly, I was taken to another scene.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:19.226
Jesus and I were suddenly in Berlin.

00:05:21.032 --> 00:05:33.440
I saw a man dressed in an expensive gray suit, a white shirt, and a nice tie getting out of a presidential-style limousine.

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:48.719
He was driven to a massive conference room in Berlin where people from all the nations of the world were gathering at a large round table.

00:05:48.719 --> 00:05:51.519
He sat at the head.

00:05:51.959 --> 00:06:09.199
I could not see his face because the Lord had blotted it out, but I could see his confident stature as the leaders listened to his plan.

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:23.420
This occurred shortly after the rapture, perhaps within a few hours.

00:06:23.420 --> 00:06:34.319
Everyone listened to him because he possessed a sense of confidence and peace similar to what the church used to provide.

00:06:36.140 --> 00:06:39.839
His presence brought a sense of calm that made everyone want to listen.

00:06:39.839 --> 00:06:50.880
Their eyes were fixed on him as he proposed a plan for a one-world currency and a chip.

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:56.239
Every world leader surrendered their power to him during that single meeting.

00:06:56.239 --> 00:06:58.820
Then I was taken back to the courthouse.

00:07:03.379 --> 00:07:13.999
There was a mandate, shown on TVs everywhere, for people to bring all Bibles to public places like police stations or town squares because owning one was no longer allowed.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:23.520
They told people they could check out their Bibles later, but anyone who did was marked as a rebel.

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:28.148
Eventually, they took the Bibles and burned them.

00:07:28.148 --> 00:07:33.720
I saw massive mounds of Bibles burning everywhere, creating huge smokestacks.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:40.919
This was happening in towns all around the world.

00:07:57.380 --> 00:07:57.640
It was against the law to have a Bible.

00:07:57.640 --> 00:08:08.370
Then I saw him take down city, state, and American flags and replace them with his own.

00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:33.531
And he put them on every courthouse over all the major public buildings that we would see an American flag, or wherever you are, your country flag, the French flag, the German flag, or the United Kingdom flag.

00:08:33.531 --> 00:08:39.100
They took those flags down and they put his flag up.

00:08:43.427 --> 00:08:54.720
And I'm going to show you right now what that flag looks like.

00:08:54.720 --> 00:09:08.740
I remember every bit of this clearly back from 2014 whenever the Lord showed me all this, what that flag looks like.

00:09:14.956 --> 00:09:22.729
And it's two swords with palm branches on the top of it, and they're golden, and there's like a globe in the middle, and there was black, white, and green, and it represented ISIS, al-Qaeda, and Hamas.

00:09:22.729 --> 00:09:31.759
All these terrorist organizations were bringing forth what they called—now I will tell you the name of what everybody called him—the Mahdi.

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:36.937
I hope I don't butcher that, but that's what they called him.

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:42.309
And everybody called this man the Mahdi.

00:09:49.640 --> 00:10:04.954
And every time you see him—look, I don't want to skip around here too much—but they put the flag up like I'm saying, and it was honor to him, the Mahdi, bringing him into power.

00:10:04.954 --> 00:10:17.440
Now I see public squares with big huge movie screens, massive movie screens that are as big as a huge building.

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:22.780
But on Fridays, everybody dresses in white garments.

00:10:22.780 --> 00:10:27.940
They dress in like white robes by law.

00:10:33.257 --> 00:10:33.623
You go and on Fridays they have lines.

00:10:40.902 --> 00:10:41.177
All the people are in lines and they worship him on Fridays with the screen.

00:10:41.177 --> 00:10:55.737
Some of it's live playback and some of it is pre-recorded because you can't worship all around the world in the daytime because it's not daytime everywhere.

00:10:55.737 --> 00:11:17.190
But they were taken, and even where—I know I told you all in a previous video, if you go look at some of my stuff before—where they worship, and it's at a big Mason temple.

00:11:17.190 --> 00:11:26.040
It's at a huge Freemason's temple.

00:11:31.760 --> 00:11:39.143
They have huge white screens all on the front of this building and this is where the people come on Fridays to worship the antichrist.

00:11:39.143 --> 00:11:49.440
They're in single file lines and they all gather in these fields.

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:59.120
Now, fill in the field—it goes way back there and it goes all the way around the building, the whole building.

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:22.780
And this is where all the townspeople from all the major towns come and they start worshiping the antichrist.

00:12:22.780 --> 00:12:43.065
I saw him worshiping in Rome at the place where the Catholics worship, by where the pope is, that square, the Catholic church and the Vatican.

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:46.994
They have major screens there.

00:13:03.713 --> 00:13:04.250
They have major screens in Europe and in Paris.

00:13:17.813 --> 00:13:18.267
It's everywhere.

00:13:18.267 --> 00:13:23.783
Even at Buckingham Palace, they had them there.

00:13:23.783 --> 00:13:27.189
I'm telling you, they're everywhere.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:33.019
And the people are required to worship on Fridays.

00:13:33.019 --> 00:13:37.359
So, that's a lot of detail with that.

00:13:38.520 --> 00:13:42.480
Now, I'm going to go another direction here to tell you all what happens.

00:13:51.320 --> 00:13:51.649
I was shown the mark of the beast.

00:13:51.649 --> 00:13:54.341
I was shown what it is.

00:14:08.731 --> 00:14:09.040
And I believe—and I'm not saying it's Neuralink—but I'm saying it is a type of Neuralink what Elon Musk is working on.

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:14.720
I'm not saying it is that, but it's that kind of technology.

00:14:18.503 --> 00:14:18.971
It's very small.

00:14:18.971 --> 00:14:28.133
But what happens is they inject it in your hand or they inject it in your forehead.

00:14:31.539 --> 00:14:54.195
And I saw all the children—and I want to say this clearly—all children were taken out of here at the rapture of the church, all the way up until what I believe was the age of 15 or 16 years old.

00:14:55.187 --> 00:15:07.070
I'm not exactly sure of the age because I did not hear anybody talking about what the age bracket of those kids was.

00:15:12.633 --> 00:15:18.941
But all the children up until the age of accountability were gone.

00:15:26.288 --> 00:15:27.133
Now, people are still going to have babies during the tribulation.

00:15:27.133 --> 00:15:30.343
Life is still going on.

00:15:30.343 --> 00:15:45.480
There are seven years of tribulation: three and a half years of not great tribulation and then three and a half years of great tribulation.

00:15:54.059 --> 00:15:54.359
But people are still creating and making babies and having families during the tribulation.

00:15:54.359 --> 00:16:07.033
So if they have a child during the tribulation, they are still here.

00:16:07.033 --> 00:16:11.839
Those children are here.

00:16:11.839 --> 00:16:17.245
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:16:17.245 --> 00:16:27.486
Remember the Bible says, "Woe to those that give suck in those days, that are breastfeeding and have children in those days.

00:16:48.525 --> 00:16:49.519
" Woe to those.

00:16:55.700 --> 00:16:58.631
It even talks about it in the word.

00:16:58.631 --> 00:17:01.303
But people are still having children.

00:17:01.589 --> 00:17:06.770
So I want you to understand that because I don't want any confusion to go, "Well, why were there kids here?

00:17:06.770 --> 00:17:11.079
" or whatever for what I'm about to tell you.

00:17:11.695 --> 00:17:16.168
Now I'm going to go, and the Lord showed me this.

00:17:16.168 --> 00:17:25.079
I saw a lot of Christians that were furious that they were left.

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:33.573
Now, I heard the Lord say this: they were upset because they preached a lukewarm gospel.

00:17:33.573 --> 00:18:02.416
They preached a sappy, watered-down grace message that they could live the way they wanted to live—a lot of people living in sin and still making it to heaven, that everything was okay with them, that they could just live like the world and still make it in the rapture of the church.

00:18:09.199 --> 00:18:09.719
And what happened?

00:18:09.719 --> 00:18:23.851
There were pastors that were preaching a compromising, lukewarm gospel that were left, and they were still here during the tribulation.

00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:39.920
And those congregation members were so mad because of the way they got preached the gospel that they were ready to kill those preachers.

00:18:44.102 --> 00:18:44.457
They were fuming mad.

00:18:47.577 --> 00:19:05.326
And I saw people that I knew that were left here during the tribulation that thought they would—I know them personally because I worked at a large church—and some of these people were major givers.

00:19:13.227 --> 00:19:29.771
And when they were left, I saw one lady in particular flipping the Lord off and giving him the finger because she was left during the tribulation and was cussing and acting crazy because she was angry she was still here, because she thought she should go.

00:19:29.771 --> 00:19:37.200
But her heart was obviously full of poison and she was vile.

00:19:37.680 --> 00:19:54.747
And I'm telling you, I saw this woman go immediately whenever the mark of the beast was given out; she was one of the first to take the mark.

00:19:54.747 --> 00:20:16.710
I remember seeing this, but there were pastors and preachers that I saw personally, and as of right now see them on TV on a weekly basis, that were left, and those congregation members were ready to string them up.

00:20:16.710 --> 00:20:18.822
It was that serious.

00:20:18.822 --> 00:20:20.289
People were upset.

00:20:20.289 --> 00:20:34.159
These pastors were on TBN and some of them were on Daystar now, and like I said, some of them are on every day.

00:20:35.908 --> 00:20:42.840
And I'm telling you, it's time to really watch who you are listening to.

00:20:42.840 --> 00:20:47.039
This is a very, very serious time.

00:20:47.039 --> 00:20:50.720
It's time to get your lamp full of oil.

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:56.817
Just like what the Bible talks about, there will be ten virgins.

00:20:56.817 --> 00:21:07.759
Five had their lamps full of oil and five were not waiting for the bridegroom to come and get them, and their lamps ran dry.

00:21:14.620 --> 00:21:18.360
It's time for you to get on fire for Jesus and have an uncompromising walk with him like you've never walked with him before.

00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:25.502
It's time to throw away the world's stuff and throw away all that garbage.

00:21:25.502 --> 00:21:28.915
Yes, we fall, but we get back up.

00:21:28.915 --> 00:21:31.350
Yes, it's by grace we're saved through faith.

00:21:31.350 --> 00:21:40.240
But I'm telling you that if you're walking in compromise and you know you're in sin and you're walking in it and you're doing it on purpose, you better get it out of your life as fast as possible.

00:21:42.897 --> 00:21:56.537
You need to go and repent and fall on the mercy seat of the Lord and say, "Father, help me to deal with this," and he'll wash you clean by the blood of the lamb and by the word of your testimony.

00:21:56.537 --> 00:21:58.034
You are free.

00:21:58.034 --> 00:22:04.190
But I'm telling you, it's not a time to play games and walk in compromise and live in the world.

00:22:04.190 --> 00:22:05.908
Yes, we mess up; things happen.

00:22:05.908 --> 00:22:11.158
But we don't consciously do it on purpose.

00:22:11.158 --> 00:22:28.799
If you say a bad word or whatever, you don't go out and say, 'I'm just going to go out and have fun.

00:22:28.799 --> 00:22:47.874
I'm going to sow my wild oats and have fun because I have Jesus in my heart and I'm going to live the way I want to and I'm going to make it.

00:22:47.874 --> 00:22:49.520
' No, you're not.

00:22:49.520 --> 00:22:53.310
You're going to get left.

00:23:00.537 --> 00:23:00.906
I'm just trying to tell you, I saw it.

00:23:00.906 --> 00:23:10.720
People say, 'There's no scripture to back that up; it's once saved, always saved.

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:17.589
' I don't believe that.

00:23:17.589 --> 00:23:22.445
After what I saw, it's not once saved, always saved.

00:23:22.445 --> 00:23:55.120
There's a remnant of people, but there are a lot of people that get left, and they are furious because they thought they could live the way they wanted to and still have the cup of blessing to go in the rapture of the church.

00:23:55.120 --> 00:23:59.920
It didn't happen that way.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:06.555
I saw those Christians try to create leaders.

00:24:06.555 --> 00:24:24.080
They were trying to make colonies, like little groups of people, and they fled to the mountains and the hills where they could get away.

00:24:24.080 --> 00:24:30.960
They grabbed what they could and went up into the hills to hide.

00:24:45.440 --> 00:24:45.920
There were literally thousands of them trying to get away because they knew what was about to happen.

00:24:45.920 --> 00:25:01.759
They knew about the Bible and had a sense of what was going on, but they just lived in compromise.

00:25:01.759 --> 00:25:08.136
I'm going to tell you how they lived.

00:25:15.580 --> 00:25:17.930
They dug holes in the side of hills—massive holes that looked like little foxholes.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:27.279
They were like big bear caves, and they were trying to keep warm in the winter.

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:36.030
The children born during the tribulation suffered greatly from starvation, cold, sickness, and disease.

00:25:36.030 --> 00:25:43.554
There were no vitamins to keep your D3 up; it was literal hell on earth.

00:25:52.480 --> 00:25:52.740
They had no way of really keeping their children safe and warm.

00:25:52.740 --> 00:26:09.200
I saw the government from all over the world start to use drones everywhere to look for anybody that did not have the mark of the beast.

00:26:27.080 --> 00:26:27.330
The chip in your forehead or your hand communicated to the drones.

00:26:35.829 --> 00:26:36.354
You could hear the drones; they were like swarms of bees.

00:26:43.304 --> 00:26:46.469
The Bible even talks about it looking like locusts coming out of a pit.

00:26:57.033 --> 00:26:57.586
I believe what John saw on the Isle of Patmos was probably these drones; that is just my opinion.

00:27:07.080 --> 00:27:07.310
The sky was buzzing with thousands of drones.

00:27:07.310 --> 00:27:20.920
They're all at a certain level—not a high altitude—just buzzing around at certain parts of the day looking for people who do not have the mark of the beast.

00:27:21.520 --> 00:27:28.754
They scan and come in packs, and you can hear them coming.

00:27:35.783 --> 00:27:37.840
They could sense fire if the Christians had a big fire while hiding in those hills.

00:27:39.590 --> 00:27:53.940
Those hills were being patrolled, but the Christians were smart and could get down in those holes and keep their heat hidden so infrared was not able to see it.

00:27:54.790 --> 00:27:56.809
They couldn't see the smoke if they had small fires.

00:27:56.809 --> 00:28:10.994
However, if they heard a gunshot or anything to kill wildlife, those drones could hear it from far away and would come to where that noise was.

00:28:10.994 --> 00:28:19.662
You could not shoot firearms to drop game like deer, elk, or cattle; so, they were starving.

00:28:32.799 --> 00:28:36.053
They would try to get fish or whatever they could find, but they would have to create a very small fire to be able to cook that food because you run out of supplies.

00:28:43.199 --> 00:28:43.519
Try seven years.

00:28:54.299 --> 00:28:54.679
This isn't just a couple of weeks living off the grid; this is seven years of hell.

00:28:54.679 --> 00:29:14.800
Some say it was only three and a half years, but even the first three and a half years were bad going into the great tribulation of the last three and a half years.

00:29:14.800 --> 00:29:17.200
It's all bad.

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:22.606
I was shown they were in the foxholes.

00:29:22.606 --> 00:29:32.879
Then Jesus and I went to another place; I watched the Christians running, trying to go from place to place.

00:29:36.270 --> 00:29:37.010
They traveled at night in the dark.

00:29:37.010 --> 00:29:45.612
There were farms where the farmers were still trying to grow crops like corn.

00:29:46.279 --> 00:29:53.415
The Christians would go out and try to steal those crops in the fields during the nighttime.

00:30:04.605 --> 00:30:04.948
But the farmer would have a dog or security system and would know they were being robbed.

00:30:04.948 --> 00:30:15.240
If the farmer was trying to be nice and didn't report what he saw to the authorities, he would be punished.

00:30:16.340 --> 00:30:25.960
A lot of people say they'll take all the guns away in America, but I saw the farmers still had guns.

00:30:25.960 --> 00:30:38.898
I heard the dogs barking and the Christians running as fast as they could to grab corn, vegetables, or chickens to try to get food.

00:30:38.898 --> 00:30:45.805
Whenever someone would see these people running and call it in, I saw them putting blocks in the roads—massive barricades.

00:30:53.786 --> 00:30:54.182
The Christians would use things to spike the tires of these people.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:30:59.239
They were in black Hummers with blue lights.

00:31:04.302 --> 00:31:12.506
I saw these massive army tank-like cars with men in solid black outfits and black shields over their faces.

00:31:16.925 --> 00:31:23.588
They would drive up in these Hummer-like cars with blue lights in them; they were almost like black lights.

00:31:37.066 --> 00:31:37.591
I remember them jumping out and the Christians running as fast as they could to get away.

00:31:40.439 --> 00:31:43.499
The men jumped out with guns that I've never seen before.

00:31:43.499 --> 00:31:50.830
I've told people about this and they said they actually exist—there are prototypes.

00:31:54.565 --> 00:32:06.204
They pulled the trigger and it was like a pulse, some kind of riot control that knocked you out for a couple of minutes.

00:32:09.496 --> 00:32:16.960
They just pointed it in a direction, and as soon as that beam hit that individual, it knocked them unconscious.

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:20.280
There was no running away.

00:32:34.080 --> 00:32:34.288
It was on the Hummers and on the men, and they would just scan the people as they were running.

00:32:40.380 --> 00:32:40.785
The people would just fall out as if they were passing out, but it didn't kill them.

00:32:40.785 --> 00:32:56.833
Then the men would walk up on them and tell them, 'Take the mark or we're going to cut your head off.

00:32:56.833 --> 00:33:14.399
' So I saw a woman and her two children that were born during the tribulation and her husband all standing there like this.

00:33:32.199 --> 00:33:32.539
They told the mother, 'If you don't take the mark and the children don't take the mark, we're going to cut those children's heads off.

00:33:32.539 --> 00:33:38.719
' And as any mother that's good would say, she was freaking out.

00:33:38.719 --> 00:33:41.600
'Don't cut my babies' heads off!

00:33:41.600 --> 00:33:43.540
I'll take the mark.

00:33:43.540 --> 00:33:51.270
' And I saw her, right before my face, take the mark of the beast.

00:33:57.146 --> 00:33:57.502
And the children took the mark of the beast.

00:34:05.560 --> 00:34:05.850
And the father said, 'No, I'll never take the mark of the beast.

00:34:05.850 --> 00:34:14.651
' And I saw those men; they pulled his head out and they had a massive sword, and they chopped his head off right before me.

00:34:17.290 --> 00:34:19.135
And I saw his head roll right before my feet.

00:34:19.135 --> 00:34:26.399
They couldn't see me, and they could not see Jesus, but Jesus told me to look.

00:34:26.399 --> 00:34:31.906
And this is something interesting: the whole time Jesus never had to speak out loud verbally to me.

00:34:38.728 --> 00:34:47.560
I could hear what he was saying by his thoughts, and he could hear what I was saying by my thoughts.

00:34:47.560 --> 00:34:56.488
I just knew it was like I was out of my body.

00:34:56.488 --> 00:35:02.160
I don't know; it was way out there, what happened.

00:35:02.160 --> 00:35:13.760
But I could smell the blood from the man that got his head cut off right before me.

